high_descs: Turn to your left, turn left at the stove, and walk to the counter.
Pick up the gold spoon from the counter.
Turn around and walk to the sink on your left.
Wash the spoon in the sink, then pick it up again.
Walk back to the counter where you got the spoon.
Open the cabinet underneath the counter and place the spoon in it.
anns.task_desc: Place a washed spoon in a cabinet.

high_descs: Turn around and walk to the stove then turn left and walk to the counter.
Pick up the ice cream scoop that's in front of you.
Turn around and walk to the right side of the sink and face it.
Wash the ice cream scoop in the sink then pick it back up and turn off the water.
Turn around and take a step then turn to your right.
Put it in the cupboard that's  second from the dishwasher and close the door.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean ice cream scoop in the cupboard.

high_descs: move to the counter to the left of the sink
pick up a scoop from the counter
move to the sink to the right of you
clean the scoop in the sink
move to the counter to the right of the stove
put the scoop in the cabinet
anns.task_desc: Put a cleaned scoop in a cabinet.
